    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in wonderful shape and has been super well-loved\u2014really reliable and still looks fantastic on the road. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin; I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, providing the precise turn-in and balance synonymous with the M-division chassis tuning. A purist\u2019s specification for those who value atmospheric induction and mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. No major issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Midnight Sapphire, which retains a deep, mirror-like gloss. While the body is straight and free of any major dents, a close inspection reveals a few minor rock chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger bumper\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The original alloy wheels are in great shape, showing only very light curb contact on the front right rim.\n\nInside, you\u2019ll find a spacious cabin appointed in Pebble Beige leather. The upholstery is supple and clean; the driver\u2019s seat shows some light creasing on the side bolster, but there are no tears or thinning. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and heated seats, functions exactly as it should. This has been a strictly non-smoking vehicle, and the interior retains a fresh, neutral scent.\n\nMechanically, this car is solid and ready for its next owner. It has been serviced religiously every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil. The engine idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. We recently replaced the brake pads and performed a multi-point inspection to ensure everything is in order. It drives straight, handles predictably, and offers a quiet, composed ride. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with respect, this is the one.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering an exceptional balance of performance and value. This model has been subject to a comprehensive professional evaluation, confirming its mechanical soundess and structural integrity. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a refined exterior finish, it represents a premier opportunity for a sophisticated owner who prioritizes reliability and documented care. This vehicle is prepared for immediate delivery, standing as a testament to quality automotive engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and has plenty of life left for its next adventure! Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this ride won't let you down. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L flat-six powerplant with VarioCam Plus. This driver\u2019s spec includes the 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been completed, including a ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a recent water pump replacement. The chassis is enhanced with Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining excellent lateral stability and damping characteristics. Braking performance is sharp thanks to four-piston monobloc calipers and fresh rotors. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the powertrain delivers a linear torque curve and the high-revving soundtrack characteristic of the M96 engine. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
